<p>
<span data-ms="22370"> Madame </span><span data-ms="22640"> Speaker, </span><span data-ms="24720"> Mr. </span><span data-ms="24950"> Vice </span><span data-ms="25180"> President, </span><span data-ms="26890"> Members </span><span data-ms="27170"> of </span><span data-ms="27260"> Congress, </span><span data-ms="29360"> and </span><span data-ms="29470"> the </span><span data-ms="29550"> First </span><span data-ms="29810"> Lady </span><span data-ms="30100"> of </span><span data-ms="30200"> the </span><span data-ms="30290"> United </span><span data-ms="30630"> States: </span>
</p>
<p><span data-ms="53880"> I’ve </span><span data-ms="54030"> come </span><span data-ms="54260"> here </span><span data-ms="54490"> tonight </span><span data-ms="55980"> not </span><span data-ms="56290"> only </span><span data-ms="56640"> to </span><span data-ms="56830"> address </span><span data-ms="57790"> the </span><span data-ms="57900"> distinguished </span><span data-ms="58530"> men </span><span data-ms="58750"> and </span><span data-ms="58900"> women </span><span data-ms="60090"> in </span><span data-ms="60240"> this </span><span data-ms="60390"> great </span><span data-ms="60640"> chamber, </span><span data-ms="62180"> but </span><span data-ms="62300"> to </span><span data-ms="62390"> speak </span><span data-ms="62750"> frankly </span><span data-ms="63330"> and </span><span data-ms="63440"> directly </span><span data-ms="64750"> to </span><span data-ms="64840"> the </span><span data-ms="64910"> men </span><span data-ms="65100"> and </span><span data-ms="65240"> women </span><span data-ms="65790"> who </span><span data-ms="65960"> sent </span><span data-ms="66260"> us </span><span data-ms="66430"> here. </span>
</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="68240"> I </span><span data-ms="68340"> know </span><span data-ms="68480"> that </span><span data-ms="68600"> for </span><span data-ms="68750"> many </span><span data-ms="68950"> Americans </span><span data-ms="69460"> watching </span><span data-ms="69920"> right </span><span data-ms="70140"> now, </span><span data-ms="70760"> the </span><span data-ms="70890"> state </span><span data-ms="71280"> of </span><span data-ms="71410"> our </span><span data-ms="71570"> economy </span><span data-ms="73020"> is </span><span data-ms="73140"> a </span><span data-ms="73200"> concern </span><span data-ms="73740"> that </span><span data-ms="73890"> rises </span><span data-ms="74670"> above </span><span data-ms="74960"> all </span><span data-ms="75190"> others. </span><span data-ms="76100"> And </span><span data-ms="76250"> rightly </span><span data-ms="76560"> so. </span><span data-ms="78170"> If </span><span data-ms="78280"> you </span><span data-ms="78540"> haven’t </span><span data-ms="78600"> been </span><span data-ms="78770"> personally </span><span data-ms="79250"> affected </span><span data-ms="79690"> by </span><span data-ms="79860"> this </span><span data-ms="80050"> recession, </span><span data-ms="81160"> you </span><span data-ms="81270"> probably </span><span data-ms="81590"> know </span><span data-ms="81800"> someone </span><span data-ms="82130"> who </span><span data-ms="82330"> has </span><span data-ms="83850"> – a </span><span data-ms="83940"> friend; </span><span data-ms="85220"> a </span><span data-ms="85300"> neighbor; </span><span data-ms="86680"> a </span><span data-ms="86740"> member </span><span data-ms="87020"> of </span><span data-ms="87090"> your </span><span data-ms="87210"> family. </span><span data-ms="89180"> You </span><span data-ms="89450"> don’t </span><span data-ms="89570"> need </span><span data-ms="89680"> to </span><span data-ms="89740"> hear </span><span data-ms="90100"> another </span><span data-ms="90430"> list </span><span da