<p><span data-ms="123090"> But </span><span data-ms="123200"> while </span><span data-ms="123420"> our </span><span data-ms="123620"> economy </span><span data-ms="124070"> may </span><span data-ms="124270"> be </span><span data-ms="124430"> weakened </span><span data-ms="125600"> and </span><span data-ms="125710"> our </span><span data-ms="125840"> confidence </span><span data-ms="126800"> shaken; </span><span data-ms="128010"> though </span><span data-ms="128120"> we </span><span data-ms="128290"> are </span><span data-ms="128430"> living </span><span data-ms="128810"> through </span><span data-ms="129050"> difficult </span><span data-ms="129710"> and </span><span data-ms="129930"> uncertain </span><span data-ms="130470"> times, </span><span data-ms="131460"> tonight </span><span data-ms="131840"> I </span><span data-ms="131970"> want </span><span data-ms="132250"> every </span><span data-ms="132550"> American </span><span data-ms="133080"> to </span><span data-ms="133200"> know </span><span data-ms="133380"> this: </span>
