<p>
<span data-ms="236660"> The </span><span data-ms="236740"> fact </span><span data-ms="237080"> is, </span><span data-ms="237480"> our </span><span data-ms="237640"> economy </span><span data-ms="238080"> did </span><span data-ms="238210"> not </span><span data-ms="238520"> fall </span><span data-ms="238730"> into </span><span data-ms="239020"> decline </span><span data-ms="239490"> overnight. </span><span data-ms="241060"> Nor </span><span data-ms="241310"> did </span><span data-ms="241470"> all </span><span data-ms="241670"> of </span><span data-ms="241770"> our </span><span data-ms="241910"> problems </span><span data-ms="242440"> begin </span><span data-ms="242890"> when </span><span data-ms="243020"> the </span><span data-ms="243090"> housing </span><span data-ms="243400"> market </span><span data-ms="243720"> collapsed </span><span data-ms="244300"> or </span><span data-ms="244360"> the </span><span data-ms="244460"> stock </span><span data-ms="244810"> market </span><span data-ms="245710"> sank. </span><span data-ms="247530"> We </span><span data-ms="247660"> have </span><span data-ms="247770"> known </span><span data-ms="248160"> for </span><span data-ms="248320"> decades </span><span data-ms="249140"> that </span><span data-ms="249280"> our </span><span data-ms="249390"> survival </span><span data-ms="250280"> depends </span><span data-ms="250730"> on </span><span data-ms="250900"> finding </span><span data-ms="251250"> new </span><span data-ms="251390"> sources </span><span data-ms="251770"> of </span><span data-ms="251860"> energy. </span><span data-ms="252560"> Yet </span><span data-ms="252730"> we </span><span data-ms="252860"> import </span><span data-ms="253310"> more </span><span data-ms="253760"> oil </span><span data-ms="253980"> today </span><span data-ms="254640"> than </span><span data-ms="254850"> ever </span><span data-ms="255140"> before. </span>
</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="256780"> The </span><span data-ms="256880"> cost </span><span data-ms="257210"> of </span><span data-ms="257280"> health </span><span data-ms="257510"> care </span><span data-ms="257760"> eats </span><span data-ms="258000"> up </span><span data-ms="258210"> more </span><span data-ms="258610"> and </span><span data-ms="258750"> more </span><span data-ms="258950"> of </span><span data-ms="259030"> our </span><span data-ms="259160"> savings </span><span data-ms="259640"> each </span><span data-ms="259820"> year, </span><span data-ms="260600"> yet </span><span data-ms="260730"> we </span><span data-ms="260850"> keep </span><span data-ms="261090"> delaying </span><span data-ms="261470"> reform. </span><span data-ms="263060"> Our </span><span data-ms="263190"> children </span><span data-ms="263630"> will </span><span data-ms="263760"> compete </span><span data-ms="264240"> for </span><span data-ms="264340"> jobs </span><span data-ms="264780"> in </span><span data-ms="264860"> a </span><span data-ms="264910"> global </span><span data-ms="265250"> economy </span><span data-ms="265730"> that </span><span data-ms="266220"> too </span><span data-ms="266390"> many </span><span data-ms="266630"> of </span><span data-ms="266730"> our </span><span data-ms="266850"> schools </span><span data-ms="267270"> do </span><span data-ms="267380"> not </span><span data-ms="267590"> prepare </span><span data-ms="267950"> them </span><span data-ms="268100"> for. </span><span data-ms="269780"> And </span><span data-ms="269870"> though </span><span data-ms="269930"> all </span><span data-ms="270210"> these </span><span data-ms="270400"> challenges </span><span data-ms="271040"> went </span><span data-ms="271350"> unsolved, </span><span data-ms="272660"> we </span><span data-ms="272820"> still </span><span data-ms="273210"> managed </span><span data-ms="273720"> to </span><span data-ms="273830"> spend </span><span data-ms="274250"> more </span><span data-ms="274520"> money </span><