</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="327280"> Well </span><span data-ms="327420"> that </span><span data-ms="327690"> day </span><span data-ms="328030"> of </span><span data-ms="328180"> reckoning </span><span data-ms="328580"> has </span><span data-ms="328910"> arrived, </span><span data-ms="329550"> and </span><span data-ms="329730"> the </span><span data-ms="329800"> time </span><span data-ms="330200"> to </span><span data-ms="330330"> take </span><span data-ms="330620"> charge </span><span data-ms="330980"> of </span><span data-ms="331100"> our </span><span data-ms="331270"> future </span><span data-ms="331690"> is </span><span data-ms="331940"> here. </span>
</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="333100"> Now </span><span data-ms="333690"> is </span><span data-ms="333800"> the </span><span data-ms="333910"> time </span><span data-ms="334460"> to </span><span data-ms="334580"> act </span><span data-ms="335080"> boldly </span><span data-ms="335520"> and </span><span data-ms="336000"> wisely </span><span data-ms="337250"> – to </span><span data-ms="337360"> not </span><span data-ms="337660"> only </span><span data-ms="337990"> revive </span><span data-ms="338480"> this </span><span data-ms="338650"> economy, </span><span data-ms="339190"> but </span><span data-ms="339340"> to </span><span data-ms="339480"> build </span><span data-ms="339730"> a </span><span data-ms="339770"> new </span><span data-ms="339950"> foundation </span><span data-ms="340580"> for </span><span data-ms="340730"> lasting </span><span data-ms="341160"> prosperity. </span><span data-ms="342580"> Now </span><span data-ms="342870"> is </span><span data-ms="342960"> the </span><span data-ms="343050"> time </span><span data-ms="343530"> to </span><span data-ms="343640"> jumpstart </span><span data-ms="344210"> job </span><span data-ms="344500"> creation, </span><span data-ms="345580"> re-start </span><span data-ms="345930"> lending, </span><span data-ms="346500"> and </span><span data-ms="346660"> invest </span><span data-ms="347120"> in </span><span data-ms="347230"> areas </span><span data-ms="347630"> like </span><span data-ms="347830"> energy, </span><span data-ms="348520"> health </span><span data-ms="348810"> care, </span><span data-ms="348960"> and </span><span data-ms="349060"> education </span><span data-ms="349590"> that </span><span data-ms="349680"> will </span><span data-ms="349840"> grow </span><span data-ms="350060"> our </span><span data-ms="350280"> economy, </span><span data-ms="351180"> even </span><span data-ms="351500"> as </span><span data-ms="351630"> we </span><span data-ms="351800"> make </span><span data-ms="352150"> hard </span><span data-ms="352410"> ch