<span data-ms="495090"> Because </span><span data-ms="495410"> of </span><span data-ms="495490"> this </span><span data-ms="495630"> plan, </span><span data-ms="496000"> families </span><span data-ms="496510"> who </span><span data-ms="496600"> are </span><span data-ms="496690"> struggling </span><span data-ms="497150"> to </span><span data-ms="497220"> pay </span><span data-ms="497390"> tuition </span><span data-ms="497840"> costs </span><span data-ms="498630"> will </span><span data-ms="498770"> receive </span><span data-ms="499170"> a </span><span data-ms="499820"> $2,500 </span><span data-ms="500560"> tax </span><span data-ms="500920"> credit </span><span data-ms="501430"> for </span><span data-ms="501680"> all </span><span data-ms="502080"> four </span><span data-ms="502310"> years </span><span data-ms="502560"> of </span><span data-ms="502660"> college. </span><span data-ms="504280"> And </span><span data-ms="509620"> Americans </span><span data-ms="510270"> who </span><span data-ms="510340"> have </span><span data-ms="510480"> lost </span><span data-ms="510830"> their </span><span data-ms="510980"> jobs </span><span data-ms="511370"> in </span><span data-ms="511460"> this </span><span data-ms="511620"> recession </span><span data-ms="512300"> will </span><span data-ms="512400"> be </span><span data-ms="512530"> able </span><span data-ms="512700"> to </span><span data-ms="512760"> receive </span><span data-ms="513200"> extended </span><span data-ms="513720"> unemployment </span><span data-ms="514290"> benefits </span><span data-ms="515250"> and </span><span data-ms="515410"> continued </span><span data-ms="515920"> health </span><span data-ms="516150"> care </span><span data-ms="516320"> coverage </span><span data-ms="516740"> to </span><span data-ms="516880"> help </span><span data-ms="517090"> them </span><span data-ms="517300"> weather </span><span data-ms="517550"> this </span><span data-ms="517720"> storm. </span>
