</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1753430"> The </span><span data-ms="1753550"> third </span><span data-ms="1753830"> challenge </span><span data-ms="1754950"> we </span><span data-ms="1755090"> must </span><span data-ms="1755330"> address </span><span data-ms="1755740"> is </span><span data-ms="1755880"> the </span><span data-ms="1756000"> urgent </span><span data-ms="1756300"> need </span><span data-ms="1756530"> to </span><span data-ms="1756620"> expand </span><span data-ms="1757510"> the </span><span data-ms="1757640"> promise </span><span data-ms="1758190"> of </span><span data-ms="1758310"> education </span><span data-ms="1758870"> in </span><span data-ms="1758980"> America. </span>
</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1760590"> In </span><span data-ms="1760680"> a </span><span data-ms="1760730"> global </span><span data-ms="1761060"> economy </span><span data-ms="1762030"> where </span><span data-ms="1762160"> the </span><span data-ms="1762230"> most </span><span data-ms="1762760"> valuable </span><span data-ms="1763210"> skill </span><span data-ms="1763570"> you </span><span data-ms="1763690"> can </span><span data-ms="1763840"> sell </span><span data-ms="1764090"> is </span><span data-ms="1764170"> your </span><span data-ms="1764340"> knowledge, </span><span data-ms="1765490"> a </span><span data-ms="1765580"> good </span><span data-ms="1765750"> education </span><span data-ms="1766360"> is </span><span data-ms="1766560"> no </span><span data-ms="1766680"> longer </span><span data-ms="1767060"> just </span><span data-ms="1767300"> a </span><span data-ms="1767350"> pathway </span><span data-ms="1767840"> to </span><span data-ms="1767930"> opportunity </span><span data-ms="1768550"> – it </span><span data-ms="1768680"> is </span><span data-ms="1768820"> a </span><span data-ms="1769120"> pre-requisite. </span>
</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1770850"> Right </span><span data-ms="1771090"> now, </span><span data-ms="1771930"> three-quarters </span><span data-ms="1772490"> of </span><span data-ms="1772650"> the </span><span data-ms="1773260"> fastest-growing </span><span data-ms="1773570"> occupations </span><span data-ms="1774780"> require </span><span data-ms="1775340"> more </span><span data-ms="1775990"> than </span><span data-ms="1776130"> a </span><span data-ms="1776160"> high </span><span data-ms="1776310"> school </span><span data-ms="1776530"> diploma. </span><span data-ms="1777870"> And </span><span data-ms="1778010"> yet, </span><span data-ms="1778200"> just </span><span data-ms="1778470"> over </span><span data-ms="1778800"> half </span><span data-ms="1779040"> of </span><span data-ms="1779150"> our </span><span data-ms="1779270"> citizens </span><span data-ms="1780030"> have </span><span data-ms="1780220"> that </span><span data-ms="1780390"> level </span><span data-ms="1780650"> of </span><span data-ms="1780730"> education. </span><span data-ms="1782270"> We </span><span data-ms="1782420"> have </span><span data-ms="1782570"> one </span><span data-ms="1782720"> of </span><span data-ms="1782810"> the </span><span data-ms="1782870"> highest </span><span data-ms="1783400"> high </span><span data-ms="1783560"> school </span><span data-ms="1783780"> dropout </span><span data-ms="1784330"> rates </span><span data-ms="1785000"> of </span><span data-ms="1785240"> any </span><span data-ms="1785520"> industrialized </span><span data-ms="1786270"> nation. </span><span data-ms="1787270"> And </span><span data-ms="1787380"> half </span><span data-ms="1787760"> of </span><span data-ms="1787860"> the </span><span data-ms="1787940"> students </span><span data-ms="1788340"> who </span><span data-ms="1788420"> begin </span><span data-ms="1788730"> college </span><span data-ms="1789560"> never </span><span data-ms="1789790"> finish. </span>
</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1791440"> This </span><span data-ms="1791600"> is </span><span data-ms="1791710"> a </span><span data-ms="1791790"> prescription </span><span data-ms="1792470"> for </span><span data-ms="1792630"> economic </span><span data-ms="1793040"> decline, </span><span data-ms="1794080"> because </span><span data-ms="1794400"> we </span><span data-ms="1794570"> know </span><span data-ms="1794830"> the </span><span data-ms="1794950"> countries </span><span data-ms="1795380"> that </span><span data-ms="1795760"> out-teach </span><span data-ms="1795990"> us </span><span data-ms="1796120"> today </span><span data-ms="1796510"> will </span><span data-ms="1796990"> out-compete </span><span data-ms="1797390"> us </span><span data-ms="1797600"> tomorrow. </span><span data-ms="1799050"> That </span><span data-ms="1799240"> is </span><span data-ms="1799360"> why </span><span data-ms="1799730"> it </span><span data-ms="1799870"> will </span><span data-ms="1800020"> be </span><span data-ms="1800160"> the </span><span data-ms="1800260"> goal </span><span data-ms="1800560"> of </span><span data-ms="1800660"> this </span><span data-ms="1800810"> administration </span><span data-ms="1801540"> to </span><span data-ms="1801670"> ensure </span><span data-ms="1802570"> that </span><span data-ms="1802810"> every </span><span data-ms="1803180"> child </span><span data-ms="1803600"> has </span><span data-ms="1803830"> access </span><span data-ms="1804710"> to </span><span data-ms="1804850"> a </span><span data-ms="1804950"> complete </span><span data-ms="1805620"> and </span><span data-ms="1805830"> competitive </span><span data-ms="1806440"> education </span><span data-ms="1807270"> – from </span><span data-ms="1807450"> the </span><span data-ms="1807560"> day </span><span data-ms="1807820"> they </span><span data-ms="1807980"> are </span><span data-ms="1808290"> born </span><span data-ms="1808650"> to </span><span data-ms="1808760"> the </span><span data-ms="1808900"> day </span><s