</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1826310"> Already, </span><span data-ms="1826790"> we </span><span data-ms="1826910"> have </span><span data-ms="1827000"> made </span><span data-ms="1827210"> an </span><span data-ms="1827270"> historic </span><span data-ms="1827670"> investment </span><span data-ms="1828680"> in </span><span data-ms="1828830"> education </span><span data-ms="1829520"> through </span><span data-ms="1830010"> the </span><span data-ms="1830190"> economic </span><span data-ms="1830590"> recovery </span><span data-ms="1830990"> plan. </span><span data-ms="1831920"> We </span><span data-ms="1832010"> have </span><span data-ms="1832100"> dramatically </span><span data-ms="1832620"> expanded </span><span data-ms="1833120"> early </span><span data-ms="1833350"> childhood </span><span data-ms="1833750"> education </span><span data-ms="1834820"> and </span><span data-ms="1834940"> will </span><span data-ms="1835050"> continue </span><span data-ms="1835500"> to </span><span data-ms="1835560"> improve </span><span data-ms="1835870"> its </span><span data-ms="1836010"> quality, </span><span data-ms="1836410"> because </span><span data-ms="1836700"> we </span><span data-ms="1836860"> know </span><span data-ms="1837610"> that </span><span data-ms="1837760"> the </span><span data-ms="1837840"> most </span><span data-ms="1838230"> formative </span><span data-ms="1838640"> learning </span><span data-ms="1839010"> comes </span><span data-ms="1839530"> in </span><span data-ms="1839670"> those </span><span data-ms="1839970"> first </span><span data-ms="1840410"> years </span><span data-ms="1840730"> of </span><span data-ms="1840860"> life. </span><span data-ms="1842140"> We </span><span data-ms="1842250"> have </span><span data-ms="1842340"> made </span><span data-ms="1842540"> college </span><span data-ms="1842890"> affordable </span><span data-ms="1843710"> for </span><span data-ms="1843870"> nearly </span><span data-ms="1844280"> seven </span><span data-ms="1844870"> million </span><s