</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1858190"> But </span><span data-ms="1858350"> we </span><span data-ms="1858480"> know </span><span data-ms="1859280"> that </span><span data-ms="1859380"> our </span><span data-ms="1859540"> schools </span><span data-ms="1860210"> don’t </span><span data-ms="1860270"> just </span><span data-ms="1860480"> need </span><span data-ms="1860640"> more </span><span data-ms="1860840"> resources. </span><span data-ms="1861760"> They </span><span data-ms="1862030"> need </span><span data-ms="1862420"> more </span><span data-ms="1862830"> reform. </span><span data-ms="1864330"> That </span><span data-ms="1864550"> is </span><span data-ms="1864700"> why </span><span data-ms="1869200"> this </span><span data-ms="1869380"> budget </span><span data-ms="1869730"> creates </span><span data-ms="1871130"> new </span><span data-ms="1871280"> incentives </span><span data-ms="1871760"> for </span><span data-ms="1871900"> teacher </span><span data-ms="1872190"> performance; </span><span data-ms="1873300"> pathways </span><span data-ms="1873910"> for </span><span data-ms="1874300"> advancement, </span><span data-ms="1875560"> and </span><span data-ms="1875780"> rewards </span><span data-ms="1876170"> for </span><span data-ms="1876310"> success. </span><span data-ms="1880360"> We’ll </span><span data-ms="1880520"> invest </span><span data-ms="1880910"> in </span><span data-ms="1881010"> innovative </span><span data-ms="1881450"> programs </span><span data-ms="1881960"> that </span><span data-ms="1882070"> are </span><span data-ms="1882180"> already </span><span data-ms="1882490"> helping </span><span data-ms="1882820"> schools </span><span data-ms="1883240"> meet </span><span data-ms="1883710"> high </span><span data-ms="1883930"> standards </span><span data-ms="1884480"> and </span><span data-ms="1884680"> close </span><span data-ms="1885010"> achievement </span><span data-ms="1885470"> gaps. </span><span data-ms="1886510"> And </span><span data-ms="1886680"> we </span><span