</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1895100"> It </span><span data-ms="1895340"> is </span><span data-ms="1895680"> our </span><span data-ms="1896010"> responsibility </span><span data-ms="1896860"> as </span><span data-ms="1897000"> lawmakers </span><span data-ms="1897790"> and </span><span data-ms="1898030"> educators </span><span data-ms="1898930"> to </span><span data-ms="1899020"> make </span><span data-ms="1899250"> this </span><span data-ms="1899400"> system </span><span data-ms="1899740"> work. </span><span data-ms="1900790"> But </span><span data-ms="1900920"> it </span><span data-ms="1900990"> is </span><span data-ms="1901070"> the </span><span data-ms="1901150"> responsibility </span><span data-ms="1901870"> of </span><span data-ms="1901970"> every </span><span data-ms="1902190"> citizen </span><span data-ms="1903180"> to </span><span data-ms="1903310"> participate </span><span data-ms="1904000"> in </span><span data-ms="1904100"> it. </span><span data-ms="1904420"> And </span><span data-ms="1905080"> so </span><span data-ms="1905220"> tonight, </span><span data-ms="1905630"> I </span><span data-ms="1905720"> ask </span><span data-ms="1906030"> every </span><span data-ms="1906320"> American </span><span data-ms="1906760"> to </span><span data-ms="1906900"> commit </span><span data-ms="1907710"> to </span><span data-ms="1907910"> at </span><span data-ms="1908070"> least </span><span data-ms="1908410"> one </span><span data-ms="1908660"> year </span><span data-ms="1908950"> or </span><span data-ms="1909130"> more </span><span data-ms="1909460"> of </span><span data-ms="1909550"> higher </span><span data-ms="1909800"> education </span><span data-ms="1910370"> or </span><span data-ms="1910590"> career </span><span data-ms="1910910"> training. </span><span data-ms="1911970"> This </span><span data-ms="1912070"> can </span><span data-ms="1912200"> be </span><span data-ms="1912380"> community </span><span data-ms="1912780"> college </span><span data-ms="1913260"> or </span><span dat