</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="1970200"> I </span><span data-ms="1983870"> know </span><span data-ms="1984100"> that </span><span data-ms="1984270"> the </span><span data-ms="1984350"> price </span><span data-ms="1984670"> of </span><span data-ms="1984760"> tuition </span><span data-ms="1985190"> is </span><span data-ms="1985310"> higher </span><span data-ms="1985640"> than </span><span data-ms="1985770"> ever, </span><span data-ms="1986780"> which </span><span data-ms="1986910"> is </span><span data-ms="1987010"> why </span><span data-ms="1987800"> if </span><span data-ms="1988050"> you </span><span data-ms="1988210"> are </span><span data-ms="1988390"> willing </span><span data-ms="1988750"> to </span><span data-ms="1988850"> volunteer </span><span data-ms="1989860"> in </span><span data-ms="1990030"> your </span><span data-ms="1990220"> neighborhood </span><span data-ms="1991200"> or </span><span data-ms="1991330"> give </span><span data-ms="1991530"> back </span><span data-ms="1991760"> to </span><span data-ms="1991860"> your </span><span data-ms="1992020"> community </span><span data-ms="1993190"> or </span><span data-ms="1993420"> serve </span><span data-ms="1993820"> your </span><span data-ms="1994050"> country, </span><span data-ms="1995280"> we </span><span data-ms="1995450"> will </span><span data-ms="1995590"> make </span><span data-ms="1995850"> sure </span><span data-ms="1996340"> that </span><span data-ms="1996500"> you </span><span data-ms="1996650"> can </span><span data-ms="1996790"> afford </span><span data-ms="1997240"> a </span><span data-ms="1997290"> higher </span><span data-ms="1997570"> education. </span><span data-ms="1999070"> And </span><span data-ms="1999260"> to </span><span data-ms="2003430"> encourage </span><span data-ms="2003960"> a </span><span data-ms="2004040"> renewed </span><span data-ms="2004440"> spirit </span><span data-ms="2004970"> of </span><span data-ms="2005030"> national </span><span data-ms="2005510"> service </span><span data-ms="200