</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="2099430"> There </span><span data-ms="2099660"> is, </span><span data-ms="2099790"> of </span><span data-ms="2099900"> course, </span><span data-ms="2100200"> another </span><span data-ms="2100470"> responsibility </span><span data-ms="2101200"> we </span><span data-ms="2101330"> have </span><span data-ms="2101540"> to </span><span data-ms="2101640"> our </span><span data-ms="2101780"> children. </span><span data-ms="2103370"> And </span><span data-ms="2103460"> that </span><span data-ms="2103650"> is </span><span data-ms="2104120"> the </span><span data-ms="2104240"> responsibility </span><span data-ms="2104930"> to </span><span data-ms="2105010"> ensure </span><span data-ms="2105670"> that </span><span data-ms="2105840"> we </span><span data-ms="2106000"> do </span><span data-ms="2106090"> not </span><span data-ms="2106740"> pass </span><span data-ms="2107060"> on </span><span data-ms="2107290"> to </span><span data-ms="2107400"> them </span><span data-ms="2107640"> a </span><span data-ms="2107680"> debt </span><span data-ms="2108180"> they </span><span data-ms="2108340"> cannot </span><span data-ms="2131930"> pay. </span><span data-ms="2136370"> With </span><span data-ms="2136590"> the </span><span data-ms="2136660"> deficit </span><span data-ms="2137100"> we </span><span data-ms="2137270"> inherited, </span><span data-ms="2147050"> the </span><span data-ms="2147150"> cost </span><span data-ms="2147740"> of </span><span data-ms="2147880"> the </span><span data-ms="2147970"> crisis </span><span data-ms="2148420"> we </span><span data-ms="2148580"> face, </span><span data-ms="2149820"> and </span><span data-ms="2150130"> the </span><span data-ms="2150510"> long-term </span><span data-ms="2150710"> challenges </span><span data-ms="2151490"> we </span><span data-ms="2151710"> must </span><span data-ms="2152170"> meet, </span><span data-ms="2153440"> it </span><span data-ms="2153610"> has </span><span data-ms="2153840"> never </span><span data-ms="21541