<p>
<span data-ms="2206770"> In </span><span data-ms="2207020"> this </span><span data-ms="2214950"> budget, </span><span data-ms="2215310"> we </span><span data-ms="2215450"> will </span><span data-ms="2215650"> end </span><span data-ms="2215850"> education </span><span data-ms="2216390"> programs </span><span data-ms="2216880"> that </span><span data-ms="2217150"> don’t </span><span data-ms="2217230"> work </span><span data-ms="2218110"> and </span><span data-ms="2218320"> end </span><span data-ms="2218550"> direct </span><span data-ms="2218910"> payments </span><span data-ms="2219320"> to </span><span data-ms="2219450"> large </span><span data-ms="2219750"> agribusinesses </span><span data-ms="2221140"> that </span><span data-ms="2221480"> don’t </span><span data-ms="2221570"> need </span><span data-ms="2221700"> them. </span><span data-ms="2229270"> We’ll </span><span data-ms="2229530"> eliminate </span><span data-ms="2230080"> the </span><span data-ms="2230410"> no-bid </span><span data-ms="2230630"> contracts </span><span data-ms="2231720"> that </span><span data-ms="2231870"> have </span><span data-ms="2231960"> wasted </span><span data-ms="2232400"> billions </span><span data-ms="2232820"> in </span><span data-ms="2232930"> Iraq, </span><span data-ms="2235320"> and </span><span data-ms="2250040"> reform </span><span data-ms="2250580"> our </span><span data-ms="2250750"> defense </span><span data-ms="2251180"> budget </span><span data-ms="2251560"> so </span><span data-ms="2251710"> that </span><span data-ms="2251920"> we’re </span><span data-ms="2251980"> not </span><span data-ms="2252220"> paying </span><span data-ms="2252600"> for </span><span data-ms="2252790"> Cold </span><span data-ms="2253300"> War-era </span><span data-ms="2253560"> weapons </span><span data-ms="2253930"> systems </span><span data-ms="2254300"> we </span><span data-ms="2254590"> don’t </span><span data-ms="2254650"> use. </span><span data-ms="2255580"> We </span><span data-ms="2258740"> w