<p>
<span data-ms="2289800"> In </span><span data-ms="2289960"> order </span><span data-ms="2290240"> to </span><span data-ms="2290350"> save </span><span data-ms="2290720"> our </span><span data-ms="2290870"> children </span><span data-ms="2291570"> from </span><span data-ms="2291750"> a </span><span data-ms="2291820"> future </span><span data-ms="2292190"> of </span><span data-ms="2292320"> debt, </span><span data-ms="2293250"> we </span><span data-ms="2293390"> will </span><span data-ms="2293560"> also </span><span data-ms="2294400"> end </span><span data-ms="2294630"> the </span><span data-ms="2294700"> tax </span><span data-ms="2295080"> breaks </span><span data-ms="2295340"> for </span><span data-ms="2295480"> the </span><span data-ms="2295550"> wealthiest </span><span data-ms="2296050"> 2% </span><span data-ms="2296430"> of </span><span data-ms="2296520"> Americans. </span><span data-ms="2298370"> But </span><span data-ms="2299980"> let </span><span data-ms="2300130"> me </span><span data-ms="2301080"> perfectly </span><span data-ms="2301400"> clear, </span><span data-ms="2302120"> because </span><span data-ms="2302560"> I </span><span data-ms="2302640"> know </span><span data-ms="2304120"> you’ll </span><span data-ms="2304390"> hear </span><span data-ms="2304710"> the </span><span data-ms="2304900"> same </span><span data-ms="2305420"> old </span><span data-ms="2305510"> claims </span><span data-ms="2306000"> that </span><span data-ms="2306210"> rolling </span><span data-ms="2306540"> back </span><span data-ms="2306780"> these </span><span data-ms="2306990"> tax </span><span data-ms="2307360"> breaks </span><span data-ms="2307650"> means </span><span data-ms="2307890"> a </span><span data-ms="2307960"> massive </span><span data-ms="2308450"> tax </span><span data-ms="2308740"> increase </span><span data-ms="2309160"> on </span><span data-ms="2309310"> the </span><span data-ms="2309380"> American </span><span data-ms="2309750"> people: </span><span data-ms="23108