<p>
<span data-ms="2364720"> To </span><span data-ms="2364920"> preserve </span><span data-ms="2365530"> our </span><span data-ms="2366010"> long-term </span><span data-ms="2366230"> fiscal </span><span data-ms="2366590"> health, </span><span data-ms="2367580"> we </span><span data-ms="2367740"> must </span><span data-ms="2367950"> also </span><span data-ms="2368400"> address </span><span data-ms="2368990"> the </span><span data-ms="2369080"> growing </span><span data-ms="2369360"> costs </span><span data-ms="2370390"> in </span><span data-ms="2370690"> Medicare </span><span data-ms="2371460"> and </span><span data-ms="2371740"> Social </span><span data-ms="2372090"> Security. </span><span data-ms="2373350"> Comprehensive </span><span data-ms="2374030"> health </span><span data-ms="2374250"> care </span><span data-ms="2374450"> reform </span><span data-ms="2374980"> is </span><span data-ms="2375160"> the </span><span data-ms="2375290"> best </span><span data-ms="2375600"> way </span><span data-ms="2375830"> to </span><span data-ms="2376020"> strengthen </span><span data-ms="2377240"> Medicare </span><span data-ms="2377800"> for </span><span data-ms="2377920"> years </span><span data-ms="2378180"> to </span><span data-ms="2378300"> come. </span><span data-ms="2378440"> And </span><span data-ms="2379270"> we </span><span data-ms="2379440"> must </span><span data-ms="2379660"> also </span><span data-ms="2379960"> begin </span><span data-ms="2380210"> a </span><span data-ms="2380270"> conversation </span><span data-ms="2381010"> on </span><span data-ms="2381130"> how </span><span data-ms="2381440"> to </span><span data-ms="2381580"> do </span><span data-ms="2381760"> the </span><span data-ms="2381880"> same </span><span data-ms="2382220"> for </span><span data-ms="2382350"> Social </span><span data-ms="2382680"> Security, </span><span data-ms="2383730"> while </span><span data-ms="2384020"> creating </span><span data-ms="2384890"> tax-free </span><span data-ms="2385180"> un