<p>
<span data-ms="2390960"> Finally, </span><span data-ms="2392260"> because </span><span data-ms="2392690"> we’re </span><span data-ms="2392750"> also </span><span data-ms="2393120"> suffering </span><span data-ms="2393690"> from </span><span data-ms="2393900"> a </span><span data-ms="2393960"> deficit </span><span data-ms="2394400"> of </span><span data-ms="2394530"> trust, </span><span data-ms="2395640"> I </span><span data-ms="2395880"> am </span><span data-ms="2396000"> committed </span><span data-ms="2396730"> to </span><span data-ms="2396830"> restoring </span><span data-ms="2397480"> a </span><span data-ms="2397610"> sense </span><span data-ms="2397990"> of </span><span data-ms="2398180"> honesty </span><span data-ms="2399110"> and </span><span data-ms="2399250"> accountability </span><span data-ms="2399980"> to </span><span data-ms="2400090"> our </span><span data-ms="2400230"> budget. </span><span data-ms="2401300"> That </span><span data-ms="2401450"> is </span><span data-ms="2401560"> why </span><span data-ms="2401780"> this </span><span data-ms="2401990"> budget </span><span data-ms="2402360"> looks </span><span data-ms="2402570"> ahead </span><span data-ms="2402860"> ten </span><span data-ms="2403070"> years </span><span data-ms="2403740"> and </span><span data-ms="2403870"> accounts </span><span data-ms="2404320"> for </span><span data-ms="2404500"> spending </span><span data-ms="2405460"> that </span><span data-ms="2405550"> was </span><span data-ms="2405700"> left </span><span data-ms="2405970"> out </span><span data-ms="2406350"> under </span><span data-ms="2406590"> the </span><span data-ms="2406700"> old </span><span data-ms="2406890"> rules </span><span data-ms="2407700"> – and </span><span data-ms="2407830"> for </span><span data-ms="2407930"> the </span><span data-ms="2408050"> first </span><span data-ms="2408330"> time, </span><span data-ms="2408570"> that </span><span data-ms="2408720"> includes </span><span data-ms="2409640"> the </span><span 