</p>
<p>
<span data-ms="2433330"> We </span><span data-ms="2434710"> are </span><span data-ms="2434930"> now </span><span data-ms="2435200"> carefully </span><span data-ms="2435610"> reviewing </span><span data-ms="2436090"> our </span><span data-ms="2436210"> policies </span><span data-ms="2436920"> in </span><span data-ms="2437080"> both </span><span data-ms="2437340"> wars, </span><span data-ms="2438230"> and </span><span data-ms="2438330"> I </span><span data-ms="2438360"> will </span><span data-ms="2438470"> soon </span><span data-ms="2438710"> announce </span><span data-ms="2439080"> a </span><span data-ms="2439150"> way </span><span data-ms="2439430"> forward </span><span data-ms="2439720"> in </span><span data-ms="2439810"> Iraq </span><span data-ms="2440640"> that </span><span data-ms="2440840"> leaves </span><span data-ms="2441070"> Iraq </span><span data-ms="2441560"> to </span><span data-ms="2441720"> its </span><span data-ms="2441900"> people </span><span data-ms="2442450"> and </span><span data-ms="2442830"> responsibly </span><span data-ms="2444080"> ends </span><span data-ms="2444630"> this </span><span data-ms="2444890"> war. </span>
